This report will enable the European Union to create a more precise legal framework with which it can enhance the safety standard by the entire food product and distribution chain .
The benefits of this text are that it proposes a method that is based on risks and controls , as well as clarifying the rules relating to animal by-products , as well as hygiene products , in addition to further rules on traceability of animal products .
I can also say to you that the previous report by Mr Schnellhardt on food hygiene ( 2002 ) had a very positive impact by making the European Wildsector aware of its responsibility .
